{"tid":990035,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港樓價第九年成為全球樓價最難負擔城市","createTime":"2019-01-21T09:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T11:07:43.000Z","uid":166622,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ae0263b710eb93de80b226c59a5e902d6b83b149","tid":990035,"uid":166622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:49:35.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】一項調查顯示，香港連續第九年成為供樓負擔最高的城市。<br />\n<br />\n一家美國顧問公司主要調查八個國家及地區，共超過300個城市。<br />\n<br />\n截至去年第三季，本港樓價中位數對家庭入息中位數比率是20.9倍，較對上一年19.4倍進一步上升。第二位是加拿大的溫哥華，第三位是澳洲悉尼，樓價對入息比率分別是12.6倍及11.7倍。<br />\n<br />\n報告指，香港在去年第三季調查時，住宅樓價的中位數是716萬9千元，家庭入息中位數則是34萬3千元。即是說，家庭入息即使完全不使用，亦需要儲蓄接近21年才可夠錢購買一個住宅，這個比率亦是調查進行15年以來的最高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/lUzIeoFYD7Dlp_OBgETUcw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/PROP-REPORT-190121-16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FlUzIeoFYD7Dlp_OBgETUcw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FPROP-REPORT-190121-16.jpg&h=89179deb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c20751dd1cb41e8046e930ceb94248536dc706d0","tid":990035,"uid":113178,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:59:11.000Z","msg":"第二名連車尾燈都見唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffabffc6c5f855525f426a3f5ea9117ae559f9a","tid":990035,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T10:16:17.000Z","msg":"係幸運定不幸"},{"pid":"45013d582db4a8d565ed3025d22e2ec7abb807eb","tid":990035,"uid":10692,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T10:17:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"752b6bd95f4e58749a74bf8f5cf641079ea7cab6","tid":990035,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bffabffc6c5f855525f426a3f5ea9117ae559f9a","tid":990035,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislik